I'd better do it myself.

284
00:14:10,890 --> 00:14:13,220
There's no need to trouble Your Highness.

285
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:15,450
Your wound shouldn't get wet.

286
00:14:16,060 --> 00:14:17,320
Let me clean your face.

287
00:14:20,220 --> 00:14:20,800
Come.

288
00:14:21,250 --> 00:14:22,490
Your Highness, there's no need for this.

289
00:14:22,490 --> 00:14:23,770
If others were to see,

290
00:14:23,800 --> 00:14:25,250
it wouldn't be appropriate.

291
00:14:25,250 --> 00:14:26,580
What's wrong with that?

292
00:14:28,130 --> 00:14:28,940
Well...

293
00:14:32,790 --> 00:14:34,490
Why do you think

294
00:14:34,730 --> 00:14:36,180
that if others were to see,

295
00:14:36,180 --> 00:14:37,780
it wouldn't be appropriate?

296
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:39,340
What exactly

297
00:14:39,580 --> 00:14:41,180
is inappropriate about it?

298
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:48,340
I kindly request you to explain in detail.

299
00:14:48,730 --> 00:14:51,100
I am eager to hear the particulars.

300
00:14:58,420 --> 00:14:59,250
It's late.

301
00:14:59,730 --> 00:15:02,390
Your Highness,
you should bathe and rest early.

302
00:15:04,820 --> 00:15:06,130
I, too, am

303
00:15:06,730 --> 00:15:08,330
tired from today's journey.

304
00:15:08,580 --> 00:15:09,840
I'd like to rest early.

305
00:15:10,580 --> 00:15:11,110
Alright.

306
00:15:11,490 --> 00:15:12,290
Someone come!

307
00:15:12,770 --> 00:15:13,580
Prepare water

308
00:15:14,820 --> 00:15:15,610
for bathing.

309
00:15:17,100 --> 00:15:17,730
Yes.

310
00:15:21,700 --> 00:15:23,300
His Highness didn't specify clearly.

311
00:15:23,300 --> 00:15:24,940
Who are bathing exactly?

312
00:15:25,100 --> 00:15:27,130
Is this water for one person

313
00:15:27,130 --> 00:15:28,610
or for two?

314
00:15:28,730 --> 00:15:29,990
And what about the tub?

315
00:15:30,130 --> 00:15:31,300
Should we prepare one tub

316
00:15:31,300 --> 00:15:32,530
or two tubs?

317
00:15:32,940 --> 00:15:34,200
Do you even need to ask?

318
00:15:34,250 --> 00:15:35,730
A couple bathing together,

319
00:15:35,730 --> 00:15:37,190
who uses two tubs for that?

320
00:15:39,100 --> 00:15:40,250
What are you so surprised about?

321
00:15:40,250 --> 00:15:41,220
Didn't you see

322
00:15:41,220 --> 00:15:43,530
it was His Highness who suggested it?

323
00:15:44,060 --> 00:15:44,940
That's right.

324
00:15:45,580 --> 00:15:47,040
How did I not think of that?

325
00:15:56,060 --> 00:15:57,060
Tan, after you.

326
00:15:58,530 --> 00:15:59,340
After me?

327
00:16:02,370 --> 00:16:03,180
Suxin,

328
00:16:04,420 --> 00:16:06,880
you've been a bit too considerate this time.

329
00:16:11,420 --> 00:16:12,940
Your Highness just said

330
00:16:13,490 --> 00:16:14,940
my wound can't get wet.

331
00:16:18,220 --> 00:16:18,950
In that case,

332
00:16:19,130 --> 00:16:20,590
I won't stand on ceremony.

333
00:16:22,940 --> 00:16:24,130
This... I...

334
00:16:24,460 --> 00:16:26,220
Your Highness, what are you doing?

335
00:16:26,220 --> 00:16:27,130
Didn't you

336
00:16:27,300 --> 00:16:29,030
want me to bathe and rest first?

337
00:16:31,300 --> 00:16:31,850
I... I...

338
00:16:44,220 --> 00:16:45,460
Tan, are you

339
00:16:45,820 --> 00:16:47,350
planning to watch me bathe?

340
00:16:58,620 --> 00:16:59,700
What's there to see?

341
00:16:59,700 --> 00:17:01,560
You're unable to perform anyway.

342
00:19:26,220 --> 00:19:27,820
Standing tall at seven feet,

343
00:19:28,940 --> 00:19:30,670
with a face like polished jade,

344
00:19:30,840 --> 00:19:33,240
every move captivating the heart and soul.

345
00:19:34,010 --> 00:19:35,530
If he doesn't have any issues in that area,

346
00:19:35,530 --> 00:19:37,660
he would truly be perfect in every way.

347
00:19:50,930 --> 00:19:52,530
Tan, your face is flushed.

348
00:19:53,940 --> 00:19:55,290
Are you feeling unwell?

349
00:19:59,260 --> 00:20:00,860
I'm just feeling a bit hot.

350
00:20:01,140 --> 00:20:02,340
Tan, don't you want to

351
00:20:03,140 --> 00:20:04,140
ask me something?

352
00:20:06,240 --> 00:20:07,330
No, I don't.

353
00:20:11,090 --> 00:20:12,090
But I...

354
00:20:14,220 --> 00:20:15,980
I have something to say to you.

355
00:20:18,070 --> 00:20:20,530
He wants to be frank with me?

356
00:20:21,330 --> 00:20:23,330
There's no need to be in such a hurry.

357
00:20:26,250 --> 00:20:27,730
What I'm about to say...

358
00:20:28,700 --> 00:20:31,420
I ask you to listen carefully to every word

359
00:20:32,090 --> 00:20:33,330
and remember it well.

360
00:20:37,220 --> 00:20:38,880
Please speak, Your Highness.

361
00:20:40,700 --> 00:20:42,420
I am in good health,

362
00:20:43,700 --> 00:20:45,300
and have no hidden ailments.

363
00:20:48,720 --> 00:20:51,520
Although I have not
been close to women in the past,

364
00:20:54,900 --> 00:20:57,030
when it comes to marital relations...

365
00:20:57,250 --> 00:20:58,530
Everything is normal.

366
00:21:02,770 --> 00:21:03,620
Normal.

367
00:21:05,520 --> 00:21:06,980
What's normal?

368
00:21:11,790 --> 00:21:13,180
You tell me.

369
00:21:21,370 --> 00:21:22,340
So you're saying

370
00:21:23,900 --> 00:21:25,940
my husband is perfectly normal.

371
00:21:26,490 --> 00:21:27,770
I'm absolutely

372
00:21:29,530 --> 00:21:30,900
normal.

373
00:21:38,050 --> 00:21:40,850
How would my husband
know that I know these things?

374
00:21:41,420 --> 00:21:42,460
In the future,

375
00:21:43,090 --> 00:21:44,620
if you have any more doubts,

376
00:21:45,130 --> 00:21:47,330
you can always come and ask me directly.

377
00:21:47,690 --> 00:21:49,530
I would be delighted to

378
00:21:50,090 --> 00:21:52,890
answer your questions
and clear up any confusion.

379
00:21:53,320 --> 00:21:54,900
After all, chasing rumors

380
00:21:56,430 --> 00:21:57,860
and gossiping

381
00:21:59,430 --> 00:22:01,330
won't solve your troubles.

382
00:23:42,660 --> 00:23:45,460
About the conclusion
of the Marquis of Cheng'en's case,

383
00:23:45,460 --> 00:23:47,060
ministers, you still need to

384
00:23:47,380 --> 00:23:49,510
work together with one heart and mind.

385
00:23:49,770 --> 00:23:52,030
Be sure not to leave any future troubles.

386
00:23:52,330 --> 00:23:54,290
I obey Your Majesty's command.

387
00:23:55,480 --> 00:23:57,730
The Ministry of Personnel has submitted

388
00:23:57,730 --> 00:24:00,180
candidates for the next
Governor of the Capital Prefecture.

389
00:24:00,180 --> 00:24:01,700
I have reviewed them all.

390
00:24:04,420 --> 00:24:05,330
Chancellors,

391
00:24:06,220 --> 00:24:08,350
do you have any preferred candidates?

392
00:24:08,940 --> 00:24:09,740
Your Majesty,

393
00:24:09,900 --> 00:24:11,860
I believe among these candidates,

394
00:24:11,860 --> 00:24:13,730
the Marquis of Jiangyang stands out.

395
00:24:13,730 --> 00:24:15,980
He is experienced,
mature, and highly respected.

396
00:24:15,980 --> 00:24:19,780
He is indeed the best choice
for Governor of the Capital Prefecture.

397
00:24:20,180 --> 00:24:20,980
Your Majesty,

398
00:24:21,180 --> 00:24:23,140
the Marquis of Jiangyang is selfless
and devoted to public service,

399
00:24:23,140 --> 00:24:24,270
upright in conduct,

400
00:24:24,290 --> 00:24:25,770
and although he has
lived in Shu for many years,

401
00:24:25,770 --> 00:24:27,770
he still has
a good reputation in the capital.

402
00:24:27,770 --> 00:24:28,570
I believe

403
00:24:28,660 --> 00:24:30,660
having him preside
over the Capital Prefecture

404
00:24:30,660 --> 00:24:32,120
is indeed the best choice.

405
00:24:33,140 --> 00:24:34,870
Since both Chancellors agree,

406
00:24:35,290 --> 00:24:37,020
let's settle on this decision.

407
00:24:43,460 --> 00:24:46,060
Your Majesty,
I have one more matter to report.

408
00:24:46,420 --> 00:24:49,090
The Marquis of Jing'an has led
the Yangxi Prefecture for many years,

409
00:24:49,090 --> 00:24:51,570
and the Prince of Dingbei
is the commander of the Dingbei Army.

410
00:24:51,570 --> 00:24:54,010
Both of them
command significant military forces.

411
00:24:54,010 --> 00:24:55,660
Now that their families
are joining in marriage,

412
00:24:55,660 --> 00:24:57,500
we should be cautious.

413
00:24:57,530 --> 00:25:00,180
I implore Your Majesty to consider
the stability of the empire.

414
00:25:00,180 --> 00:25:02,010
Remove the commander of Yangxi Prefecture.

415
00:25:02,010 --> 00:25:03,870
Reassign the Marquis of Jing'an.

416
00:25:07,600 --> 00:25:08,700
You all in Changming Hall

417
00:25:08,700 --> 00:25:10,230
are used to verbal battles,

418
00:25:10,240 --> 00:25:11,860
thinking that being a military commander

419
00:25:11,860 --> 00:25:13,990
is as casual and easy as giving advice.

420
00:25:14,080 --> 00:25:16,110
You think you can
just replace someone at will?

421
00:25:16,110 --> 00:25:17,420
Transferring the military tally

422
00:25:17,420 --> 00:25:19,220
may seem like a mere formality,

423
00:25:19,640 --> 00:25:21,400
but I ask you, in the entire court,

424
00:25:21,400 --> 00:25:23,490
who can take on this military tally,

425
00:25:24,270 --> 00:25:26,130
stabilize the morale of the army,

426
00:25:26,430 --> 00:25:28,890
and keep the ambitious barbarians in check?

427
00:25:39,250 --> 00:25:40,180
Your Majesty,

428
00:25:40,570 --> 00:25:41,420
actually, after my daughter's

429
00:25:41,420 --> 00:25:43,220
wedding with the Prince of Dingbei,

430
00:25:43,220 --> 00:25:45,420
I have already considered this matter.

431
00:25:46,380 --> 00:25:48,250
I am approaching
the end of my natural lifespan.

432
00:25:48,250 --> 00:25:51,140
My energy is failing,
and I suffer from many ailments.

433
00:25:51,140 --> 00:25:53,340
I humbly request Your Majesty's mercy.

434
00:25:53,460 --> 00:25:56,530
Please allow me
to remain in the capital to recuperate.

435
00:25:56,860 --> 00:25:59,010
As for the position
of commander in Yangxi Prefecture,

436
00:25:59,010 --> 00:26:01,090
I would never dare
to cling to this position.

437
00:26:01,090 --> 00:26:04,460
I implore Your Majesty
to select another capable individual

438
00:26:04,460 --> 00:26:06,520
to entrust with this important task.

439
00:26:07,930 --> 00:26:10,680
Lord Ming has governed
Yangxi Prefecture for many years.

440
00:26:10,680 --> 00:26:11,940
Moving him carelessly

441
00:26:12,850 --> 00:26:14,650
would indeed be inappropriate.

442
00:26:15,460 --> 00:26:17,060
And choosing a new commander

443
00:26:18,050 --> 00:26:18,860
should not

444
00:26:19,620 --> 00:26:20,940
be done hastily.

445
00:26:22,050 --> 00:26:22,940
So

446
00:26:24,010 --> 00:26:26,210
everything will remain as it is for now.

447
00:26:26,290 --> 00:26:28,380
When a new commander is appointed,

448
00:26:28,980 --> 00:26:31,460
Lord Ming, you can
then hand over the military tally

449
00:26:31,460 --> 00:26:33,720
and be reassigned to stay in the capital.

450
00:26:34,380 --> 00:26:36,010
I obey Your Majesty's order.

451
00:26:36,850 --> 00:26:37,650
Your Majesty,

452
00:26:38,570 --> 00:26:40,660
since Your Majesty has made a decision,

453
00:26:40,660 --> 00:26:42,530
regarding the reassignment
of the Marquis of Jing'an,

454
00:26:42,530 --> 00:26:44,590
we should also discuss it in advance.

455
00:26:45,420 --> 00:26:46,220
In my opinion,

456
00:26:46,620 --> 00:26:49,090
the Marquis of Jing'an has guarded
Yangxi Prefecture for many years,

457
00:26:49,090 --> 00:26:50,820
with great merit and hard work.

458
00:26:51,260 --> 00:26:52,730
This time, during his stay in the capital,

459
00:26:52,730 --> 00:26:54,930
his rank should not be lowered too much,

460
00:26:55,010 --> 00:26:57,410
to avoid disheartening the border troops.

461
00:26:57,770 --> 00:26:58,770
Of course.

462
00:26:59,460 --> 00:27:00,730
In the twelve departments
of the Privy Council,

463
00:27:00,730 --> 00:27:02,530
the Southern and Hedong departments

464
00:27:02,530 --> 00:27:03,790
still have vacancies.

465
00:27:03,980 --> 00:27:05,010
Why don't we

466
00:27:05,180 --> 00:27:07,380
transfer the Marquis of Jing'an
to the Privy Council

467
00:27:07,380 --> 00:27:10,780
and appoint him
as the Deputy Envoy of these two departments?

468
00:27:11,460 --> 00:27:12,460
This proposal

469
00:27:13,170 --> 00:27:14,660
is quite appropriate.

470
00:27:17,460 --> 00:27:20,660
I thank Your Majesty
for your great kindness.

471
00:27:30,980 --> 00:27:31,380
Sir,

472
00:27:32,220 --> 00:27:33,250
on the eve of your wedding,

473
00:27:33,250 --> 00:27:34,620
Vice Minister Liu did indeed leave the city.

474
00:27:34,620 --> 00:27:36,950
He didn't return until the following day.

475
00:27:48,410 --> 00:27:49,820
As per your instructions, Sir,

476
00:27:49,820 --> 00:27:51,140
I have found information on Liu Mo

477
00:27:51,140 --> 00:27:52,720
in the records of the Jia Archive.

478
00:27:52,720 --> 00:27:53,380
There are records of his life

479
00:27:53,380 --> 00:27:54,460
only from when he entered the capital

480
00:27:54,460 --> 00:27:55,320
at the age of 12.

481
00:27:55,940 --> 00:27:57,940
There are only a few brief notes
about his earlier life,

482
00:27:57,940 --> 00:27:59,090
merely mentioning
that after his parents passed away,

483
00:27:59,090 --> 00:28:00,550
he drifted to the capital.

484
00:28:02,250 --> 00:28:03,450
Keep investigating.

485
00:28:04,460 --> 00:28:06,050
No one can completely erase

486
00:28:06,550 --> 00:28:07,770
their past.

487
00:28:08,250 --> 00:28:08,980
Understood.

488
00:28:16,700 --> 00:28:18,630
There's some travel money in here.

489
00:28:18,860 --> 00:28:20,180
I heard your mother

490
00:28:20,460 --> 00:28:22,140
has been ill these past two days.

491
00:28:22,140 --> 00:28:23,250
So I had Suxin

492
00:28:23,530 --> 00:28:25,130
add some tonic herbs inside.

493
00:28:25,490 --> 00:28:27,550
Me and my mother thank Your Highness.

494
00:28:28,940 --> 00:28:29,570
Jiurou,

495
00:28:30,010 --> 00:28:32,610
there's no need
for such formality between us.

496
00:28:32,860 --> 00:28:35,090
If it weren't for His Highness
and Your Highness,

497
00:28:35,090 --> 00:28:37,890
my mother and I
would surely have no way to survive.

498
00:28:38,050 --> 00:28:40,460
Please convey to His Highness on my behalf,

499
00:28:40,700 --> 00:28:41,490
thank him

500
00:28:42,420 --> 00:28:44,660
for giving my mother and me

501
00:28:44,660 --> 00:28:46,220
a chance at a new life.

502
00:28:46,940 --> 00:28:49,070
I will certainly pass on your message.

503
00:28:51,140 --> 00:28:52,180
I just don't know

504
00:28:54,620 --> 00:28:56,460
if we'll have the chance

505
00:28:57,090 --> 00:28:58,050
to meet again.

506
00:28:59,180 --> 00:29:01,180
Your Highness, please rest assured,

507
00:29:01,180 --> 00:29:02,460
my mother and I will

508
00:29:02,490 --> 00:29:04,050
take good care of ourselves

509
00:29:04,090 --> 00:29:05,890
and live peacefully from now on.

510
00:29:05,900 --> 00:29:07,360
If I have the opportunity,

511
00:29:07,570 --> 00:29:09,830
I will certainly write to Your Highness.

512
00:29:10,250 --> 00:29:11,050
Now,

513
00:29:11,290 --> 00:29:12,090
I don't have many

514
00:29:12,090 --> 00:29:13,690
valuable possessions left.

515
00:29:14,700 --> 00:29:15,700
I can only offer this

516
00:29:15,700 --> 00:29:18,330
silk handkerchief I embroidered myself
as a gift to Your Highness

517
00:29:18,330 --> 00:29:20,130
as a small token of my gratitude.

518
00:29:25,660 --> 00:29:26,770
I will cherish

519
00:29:28,570 --> 00:29:30,290
this handkerchief dearly.

520
00:29:32,700 --> 00:29:33,560
Your Highness,

521
00:29:33,730 --> 00:29:35,010
it's getting late.

522
00:29:35,250 --> 00:29:37,620
I must take my leave now.

523
00:29:39,250 --> 00:29:40,710
Take care, Your Highness.

524
00:29:59,860 --> 00:30:02,180
Grandmother, I won't marry! I won't marry!

525
00:30:02,180 --> 00:30:03,640
I'd rather die than marry!

526
00:30:03,940 --> 00:30:06,270
I'm only thinking of your best interests.

527
00:30:08,460 --> 00:30:09,980
If you truly cared for me,

528
00:30:10,540 --> 00:30:12,530
how could you let me
become someone's second wife?

529
00:30:12,530 --> 00:30:13,710
Moreover, that Gao Chen

530
00:30:13,710 --> 00:30:15,230
is a notorious womanizer

531
00:30:15,250 --> 00:30:16,250
and a lecher.

532
00:30:17,240 --> 00:30:18,330
If I marry him,

533
00:30:18,920 --> 00:30:20,700
the rest of my life will be ruined.

534
00:30:20,700 --> 00:30:21,660
Silence!

535
00:30:24,380 --> 00:30:26,490
Greetings, Empress Dowager.

536
00:30:27,330 --> 00:30:28,090
Princess.

537
00:30:28,220 --> 00:30:28,860
Uncle.

538
00:30:29,700 --> 00:30:31,490
Please speak up for me.

539
00:30:32,770 --> 00:30:33,940
Grandmother insists that I marry

540
00:30:33,940 --> 00:30:35,920
the son of the Marquis of Jiangyang
as his second wife.

541
00:30:35,920 --> 00:30:37,140
As a noble princess,

542
00:30:37,660 --> 00:30:40,860
how can I suffer
such humiliation by marrying beneath me?

543
00:30:41,050 --> 00:30:43,310
Moreover, that Gao Chen is not a good man.

544
00:30:46,220 --> 00:30:46,980
Princess,

545
00:30:48,250 --> 00:30:49,460
this marriage,

546
00:30:49,700 --> 00:30:50,940
whether for you

547
00:30:51,250 --> 00:30:52,700
or for the Su family,

548
00:30:52,860 --> 00:30:54,860
is already the best arrangement.

549
00:30:59,250 --> 00:31:01,440
So you've all discussed this already,

550
00:31:01,490 --> 00:31:03,490
and I'm the only one kept in the dark.

551
00:31:05,010 --> 00:31:06,140
Today, crying and making a scene

552
00:31:06,140 --> 00:31:07,290
won't help.

553
00:31:08,090 --> 00:31:10,090
This matter is not for you to decide.

554
00:31:22,810 --> 00:31:24,530
His Majesty has already decided.

555
00:31:24,530 --> 00:31:27,730
The Marquis of Jiangyang will succeed
as the Governor of the Capital Prefecture.

556
00:31:27,730 --> 00:31:29,660
The marriage
between the Princess and Gao Chen

557
00:31:29,660 --> 00:31:31,730
cannot afford any mistakes.

558
00:31:32,780 --> 00:31:34,460
I will make arrangements

559
00:31:34,490 --> 00:31:36,490
for Nianci and Gao Chen to meet,

560
00:31:37,150 --> 00:31:38,660
