842
00:41:44,780 --> 00:41:45,570
and you put it to paper.

843
00:41:45,570 --> 00:41:46,430
How about that?

844
00:41:46,850 --> 00:41:47,780
No problem.

845
00:41:48,750 --> 00:41:52,280
[Prince of Dingbei's Mansion]

846
00:42:04,900 --> 00:42:07,050
I heard you're going to write a story

847
00:42:07,050 --> 00:42:08,100
with Miss Bai.

848
00:42:09,980 --> 00:42:11,510
How did you know about this?

849
00:42:11,860 --> 00:42:14,660
Mr. Fu mentioned it
when I returned to the mansion.

850
00:42:17,010 --> 00:42:20,050
A large number of refugees
suddenly flooded into the capital.

851
00:42:20,050 --> 00:42:22,580
I wonder what the situation
is like in Lizhou.

852
00:42:23,130 --> 00:42:25,300
The noble ladies
are raising funds for charity.

853
00:42:25,300 --> 00:42:26,110
Minmin and I

854
00:42:26,130 --> 00:42:27,930
should also do our part.

855
00:42:28,650 --> 00:42:30,650
Besides, I'd like to allocate
some of the profits from Cuojin Pavilion

856
00:42:30,650 --> 00:42:32,460
and Jinxiu Workshop

857
00:42:32,460 --> 00:42:33,740
to aid the refugees.

858
00:42:33,740 --> 00:42:35,200
I hope you'll approve, Xu.

859
00:42:37,170 --> 00:42:38,370
You're kind-hearted

860
00:42:38,530 --> 00:42:39,780
and considerate of the people.

861
00:42:39,780 --> 00:42:41,530
I naturally approve.

862
00:42:42,980 --> 00:42:44,010
Thank you, Xu.

863
00:42:46,530 --> 00:42:47,950
But before that,

864
00:42:48,090 --> 00:42:49,650
You need to eat properly.

865
00:42:49,860 --> 00:42:51,780
If you can't take care of yourself,

866
00:42:51,780 --> 00:42:53,170
how can you help others?

867
00:43:20,420 --> 00:43:21,110
Your...

868
00:43:33,170 --> 00:43:34,300
His Majesty has appointed my father-in-law

869
00:43:34,300 --> 00:43:35,530
to provide disaster relief in Lizhou.

870
00:43:35,530 --> 00:43:36,930
He's departing tonight.

871
00:43:37,050 --> 00:43:38,650
I'm going to see him off.

872
00:43:38,780 --> 00:43:40,570
Would you like to come along?

873
00:43:45,050 --> 00:43:46,270
Lizhou isn't far.

874
00:43:46,420 --> 00:43:48,750
Father should be back soon.

875
00:43:48,820 --> 00:43:50,040
I won't go.

876
00:43:50,180 --> 00:43:51,030
Suxin,

877
00:43:51,050 --> 00:43:52,450
go fetch the fur knee pads

878
00:43:52,450 --> 00:43:53,710
I bought a few days ago.

879
00:43:54,530 --> 00:43:55,280
Yes.

880
00:43:59,010 --> 00:44:00,870
The flooding in Lizhou is severe.

881
00:44:00,980 --> 00:44:03,780
I'm afraid Father's
old leg injury might flare up.

882
00:44:03,940 --> 00:44:04,740
Please, Xu,

883
00:44:04,740 --> 00:44:06,460
take these knee pads to Father.

884
00:44:06,460 --> 00:44:08,720
Tell Father to take good care of himself.

885
00:44:11,100 --> 00:44:11,700
Okay.

